snippet.title: Food Fantasy: Pre-registration available now!
snippet.description:
Food Fantasy Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/foodfantasygame/

Pre-registration IOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/food-fantasy/id1366072359?mt=8(Please update to IOS 11.2 for pre-registration and only available for America, Europe and Southeast Asia players)

Pre-registration Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.egg.foodandroid

🎉🎉🎉"Food Fantasy" has begun pre-registration on Google Play and App Store!! 🎉🎉🎉

Collect Food Souls from all over the world & personalize your restaurant.

Experience awesome Japanese and English voice overs! 
Come and start your RPG food adventure! 🍾🍽🍖
